{"tid":878521,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"動物台持棒部揸車去大洗聖巡遊記","createTime":"2018-10-27T08:10:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-27T12:44:22.000Z","uid":8307,"like":5,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"a8a6b0fe086afaac39d74074e9c4d189ec37244b","tid":878521,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T08:10:45.000Z","msg":"今個星期唔去船p了,決定揸車去大洗旅下行<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VaJQvhh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVaJQvhh.jpg&h=25940730&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢個我地駕駛員,會然上條當麻(阻治)<br />\n手車好得揸到時速50都好定<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/94LO1p1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F94LO1p1.jpg&h=d9d2e6fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n炮手19仔(會然星見純那),睇個樣都知佢好麻煩<br />\n不過控炮幾好<br />\n<br />\n車長就緊係我做,相就唔貼了<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/d/dc/Bundesarchiv_Bild_183-J08365%2C_Ausbildung%2C_%C3%9Cberrollen_durch_Panzer.jpg/220px-Bundesarchiv_Bild_183-J08365%2C_Ausbildung%2C_%C3%9Cberrollen_durch_Panzer.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fthumb%2Fd%2Fdc%2FBundesarchiv_Bild_183-J08365%252C_Ausbildung%252C_%25C3%259Cberrollen_durch_Panzer.jpg%2F220px-Bundesarchiv_Bild_183-J08365%252C_Ausbildung%252C_%25C3%259Cberrollen_durch_Panzer.jpg&h=830498e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我地租左架四號,準備由柏林直駛去大洗<br />\n<br />\n好想見到我女友<img src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-UakTFgS392w/U32fQKF1KOI/AAAAAAAABQg/1P2P0qTUulk/s1600/188.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-UakTFgS392w%2FU32fQKF1KOI%2FAAAAAAAABQg%2F1P2P0qTUulk%2Fs1600%2F188.png&h=8f96cee3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oVtpzL1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoVtpzL1.jpg&h=6f5c3972&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"82e7cb9389eab1f8bf43f1aa2b9fa8ab3b717048","tid":878521,"uid":53196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T08:12:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e922be59f1b98dfdf3343fc33bb1ea98db0cc682","tid":878521,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T08:14:25.000Z","msg":"第一站波蘭<br />\n<img src=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/660/cpsprodpb/C266/production/_85766794_thinkstockphotos-92821902-1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F660%2Fcpsprodpb%2FC266%2Fproduction%2F_85766794_thinkstockphotos-92821902-1.jpg&h=bee02d3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n沿途上冇咩特別,但係出名麻煩既19仔厭波蘭冇野好食<br />\n我就覺得應該係佢唔啱口味姐<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VwyQvkV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVwyQvkV.png&h=8696ef57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n叫左個餐,唔識波蘭啲文,唔知咩黎<br />\n幾香口"},{"pid":"012b8e3e0ea5bab1ad5ef511288706227cecb279","tid":878521,"uid":34293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T08:15:27.000Z","msg":"我gta山路練左兩年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccab143ddc8593e6cdd2f3d8c71a25a83fa132c3","tid":878521,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T08:15:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/8/82/Heinkel_He_111_during_the_Battle_of_Britain.jpg/710px-Heinkel_He_111_during_the_Battle_of_Britain.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fthumb%2F8%2F82%2FHeinkel_He_111_during_the_Battle_of_Britain.jpg%2F710px-Heinkel_He_111_during_the_Battle_of_Britain.jpg&h=7201d7e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n路程中見到上空有he111飛過"},{"pid":"e105e5a8eb8a25b22cb7713e10143819db1854cb","tid":878521,"uid":94167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T08:17:13.000Z","msg":"你隻腳好撚臭，可唔可以縮開"},{"pid":"523db2ad5809d2d0a0921c25001c43aa0d9e1314","tid":878521,"uid":8307,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T08:22:00.000Z","msg":"中間就冇咩好講了<br />\n見冇咩人回,直接入關鍵部份先<br />\n<br />\n入到俄羅斯領地範圍<br />\n好唔好彩見到架is-2<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.tanks-encyclopedia.com/ww2/soviet/photos/is-2m-Berlin1945.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.tanks-encyclopedia.com%2Fww2%2Fsoviet%2Fphotos%2Fis-2m-Berlin1945.png&h=9a13e321&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n對我地好有敵意<br />\n比人打到鳩都甩埋<br />\n好彩冇直接擊穿到車入面,唔係既話成班變燒豬<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/10X2muV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F10X2muV.png&h=5e96d91f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n決定返去換架豹式擇日再戰"},{"pid":"fd4dd327e90dc145f634e6ee7d4865f4c9d7c7f0","tid":878521,"uid":94167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T08:24:38.000Z","msg":"樓主條盲鳩咁大部IS都見唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搞到我地又要返屋企"},{"pid":"eeb2c5e0fff719f4e8ff648f8f206440deea5af2","tid":878521,"uid":197162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T08:26:08.000Z","msg":"on 99"},{"pid":"94150e404636279808ca866dcdbf789b7d0952a5","tid":878521,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fd4dd327e90dc145f634e6ee7d4865f4c9d7c7f0","tid":878521,"uid":94167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T08:24:38.000Z","msg":"樓主條盲鳩咁大部IS都見唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搞到我地又要返屋企"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T08:27:03.000Z","msg":"咪能嘈"},{"pid":"e20d16c213915686777e42f9c58afc89d11b40d5","tid":878521,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T10:03:17.000Z","msg":"揸兩架虎式都比人打到哭"},{"pid":"e94f16e1b16ead3e9836f8f03673d39c3c336588","tid":878521,"uid":150609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T10:30:37.000Z","msg":"m記驚現on9仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15b214e39da3